1
00:00:00,767 --> 00:00:02,433
[DRAMATIC TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

2
00:00:08,133 --> 00:00:09,733
- Jasmine! Jasmine!
- Jasmine?

3
00:00:09,867 --> 00:00:11,067
The window is closing.

4
00:00:11,200 --> 00:00:13,633
If you know any potential
donors,

5
00:00:13,767 --> 00:00:15,233
we really need to move soon.

6
00:00:15,367 --> 00:00:16,333
What are you doing here?

7
00:00:16,467 --> 00:00:17,667
I am here to plead.

8
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:19,800
We really need Ashley
to get tested.

9
00:00:19,933 --> 00:00:20,900
I will not allow it.

10
00:00:21,033 --> 00:00:23,367
I will not gamble
my child's safety.

11
00:00:23,500 --> 00:00:25,267
Leave! Leave!

12
00:00:25,400 --> 00:00:28,233
If you want to secure
your child's future,

13
00:00:28,367 --> 00:00:29,967
there is one thing you can do.

14
00:00:30,100 --> 00:00:32,300
If you need to beg Thea, do it.

15
00:00:32,433 --> 00:00:34,967
I no longer care
what else is thrown in my face

16
00:00:35,133 --> 00:00:37,000
because I want my child to live.

17
00:00:37,133 --> 00:00:40,333
Do you really want
to help Jasmine?

18
00:00:41,267 --> 00:00:42,067
Consent form,

19
00:00:42,200 --> 00:00:43,900
I am agreeing
to have Ashley tested.

20
00:00:44,367 --> 00:00:45,500
This is just a test.

21
00:00:45,633 --> 00:00:48,467
It does not mean she will
automatically donate

22
00:00:48,600 --> 00:00:49,867
and Edward does not know
about this yet.

23
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:51,267
Where did you come from?

24
00:00:51,400 --> 00:00:52,800
So, are there results already?

25
00:00:52,933 --> 00:00:54,300
What did the doctor say?

26
00:00:55,333 --> 00:01:01,000
[DRAMATIC TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

27
00:01:01,133 --> 00:01:09,800
[MUSIC CONTINUES...]

28
00:01:14,333 --> 00:01:23,133
[MUSIC CONTINUES...]

29
00:01:25,433 --> 00:01:30,567
[DRAMATIC TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

30
00:01:40,600 --> 00:01:42,133
Have you eaten?

31
00:01:42,300 --> 00:01:44,500
This is the spare keycard
to our room.

32
00:01:44,633 --> 00:01:48,333
In case you want to come here.

33
00:01:48,467 --> 00:01:49,333
I am leaving now.

34
00:01:49,467 --> 00:01:50,767
I will just visit again.

35
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,700
Edward, please.

36
00:01:54,767 --> 00:01:56,567
Let us try to fix this.

37
00:01:57,467 --> 00:01:59,167
For Ashley, for our family.

38
00:01:59,300 --> 00:02:00,200
Thea!

39
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,600
Now you want to fix this?

40
00:02:03,733 --> 00:02:05,167
Now that you and Paolo are done?

41
00:02:05,300 --> 00:02:06,933
Now that I am broken?
You are broken?

42
00:02:07,067 --> 00:02:08,800
You were kicked out
of the mansion?

43
00:02:08,933 --> 00:02:10,767
Now that you have fallen,
you want to come back to me?

44
00:02:11,900 --> 00:02:15,600
Thea, I do not want
to be your spare tire.

45
00:02:15,767 --> 00:02:17,833
I may not have
achieved much before,

46
00:02:17,967 --> 00:02:20,433
but I did not deserve
what you did to me.

47
00:02:20,567 --> 00:02:22,067
Do you know why
I came back here?

48
00:02:23,633 --> 00:02:24,733
For Ashley.

49
00:02:25,733 --> 00:02:26,800
For my child.

50
00:02:27,900 --> 00:02:30,600
So do not expect
that we will reconcile.

51
00:02:32,167 --> 00:02:33,367
[DOORBELL RINGS]

52
00:02:36,833 --> 00:02:40,767
[PENSIVE MUSIC PLAYING]

53
00:02:41,700 --> 00:02:43,933
- Edward.
- What are you doing here?

54
00:02:44,067 --> 00:02:45,500
Sorry.

55
00:02:45,633 --> 00:02:48,367
I really found a way
to find you.

56
00:02:48,533 --> 00:02:49,867
I am not here to fight.

57
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,800
I am here to beg.

58
00:02:53,433 --> 00:02:54,467
For Marj.

59
00:02:55,667 --> 00:02:57,233
Especially for Jasmine.

60
00:02:58,733 --> 00:02:59,767
Ashley.

61
00:03:00,833 --> 00:03:04,100
She is our only hope
for Jasmine to live.

62
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:11,567
[MUSIC CONTINUES...]

63
00:03:13,900 --> 00:03:16,000
We really need Ashley
to get tested.

64
00:03:16,133 --> 00:03:17,900
Because if they match,

65
00:03:18,967 --> 00:03:21,200
that is Jasmine's best chance

66
00:03:21,367 --> 00:03:23,967
for a bone marrow transplant.

67
00:03:24,100 --> 00:03:26,433
After you exiled us,

68
00:03:26,567 --> 00:03:27,900
you suddenly want
to use my child

69
00:03:28,033 --> 00:03:30,067
for your child with Marj?

70
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:31,600
Edward, please.

71
00:03:34,267 --> 00:03:36,300
We have no one else to turn to.

72
00:03:37,967 --> 00:03:38,933
No.

73
00:03:39,067 --> 00:03:40,367
I'm sorry.

74
00:03:40,500 --> 00:03:43,133
I will not allow
my child to get tested.

75
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:44,900
Edward, please.

76
00:03:47,067 --> 00:03:48,500
I do not want my child to die

77
00:03:48,633 --> 00:03:50,900
without trying everything.

78
00:03:56,667 --> 00:03:59,600
Here, water.

79
00:03:59,733 --> 00:04:03,300
Jasmine, we already talked
to Ashley.

80
00:04:03,433 --> 00:04:06,700
Once we get their consent,

81
00:04:06,833 --> 00:04:11,167
we can have her tested
for the bone marrow transplant.

82
00:04:11,300 --> 00:04:13,933
My child, there is a big chance
that you will match.

83
00:04:15,367 --> 00:04:17,367
I do not want to.

84
00:04:17,500 --> 00:04:19,333
What do you not want?

85
00:04:19,467 --> 00:04:21,867
I do not want her
to be my donor.

86
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:24,167
That feels weird, right?

87
00:04:24,300 --> 00:04:25,800
After everything?

88
00:04:25,933 --> 00:04:28,300
After her mom was the reason
why things got messy on us,

89
00:04:28,467 --> 00:04:30,667
then she is the one
who's going to save me?

90
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:33,267
Jasmine, if there is a chance
to help us,

91
00:04:33,400 --> 00:04:35,200
we will take it.

92
00:04:35,333 --> 00:04:38,533
And, Mom, she kind of
betrayed me with Xander.

93
00:04:38,667 --> 00:04:42,133
I just do not want to feel like
I owe her something.

94
00:04:42,267 --> 00:04:45,233
My child, your life
is at stake here.

95
00:04:45,367 --> 00:04:46,667
I know.

96
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,133
But that does not mean

97
00:04:48,267 --> 00:04:50,633
I do not have feelings, right?

98
00:04:50,767 --> 00:04:53,333
Jasmine, this is no longer
about your feelings.

99
00:04:54,333 --> 00:04:55,967
But I feel like Ashley
should not be the one

100
00:04:56,100 --> 00:04:57,233
who could help us.

101
00:04:57,367 --> 00:05:00,467
Ashley is too young
to be a donor.

102
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:03,233
I will not gamble
my child's safety.

103
00:05:03,400 --> 00:05:05,533
Ashley is not your child.

104
00:05:05,667 --> 00:05:07,233
You know I am the real father.

105
00:05:07,367 --> 00:05:08,800
You have a lot of nerve.

106
00:05:10,033 --> 00:05:11,567
Where were you then?
Where were you then?

107
00:05:12,633 --> 00:05:15,200
You lived without Ashley for
years.

108
00:05:16,533 --> 00:05:17,700
And now that you need her,

109
00:05:17,833 --> 00:05:19,233
you suddenly want to act
like a father?

110
00:05:20,433 --> 00:05:21,800
I took care of her.

111
00:05:21,933 --> 00:05:23,167
I raised her.

112
00:05:23,300 --> 00:05:24,633
I still have the right to her.

113
00:05:24,767 --> 00:05:26,033
I am her legal father.

114
00:05:26,167 --> 00:05:28,700
So my decision is,
I will not allow it.

115
00:05:30,367 --> 00:05:32,567
No, Edward, please.

116
00:05:32,700 --> 00:05:33,667
Thea.

117
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:35,567
- Leave now, leave now.
- I am begging you.

118
00:05:35,733 --> 00:05:38,233
Leave now, leave now!
Leave now, leave now!

119
00:05:38,367 --> 00:05:43,167
[INTENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

120
00:05:45,333 --> 00:05:48,167
Now is not the time
to be choosy, Jasmine.

121
00:05:49,400 --> 00:05:51,333
Do you think I have a choice?

122
00:05:51,467 --> 00:05:55,600
Did I want to beg
her mother to help us?

123
00:05:57,367 --> 00:05:59,367
I swallow my pride every time

124
00:05:59,500 --> 00:06:00,967
I speak to your father

125
00:06:01,100 --> 00:06:04,000
and approach the woman who
ruined our family.

126
00:06:04,133 --> 00:06:07,300
Because I am scared, Jasmine,
I do not want you to die.

127
00:06:07,467 --> 00:06:09,333
Because of those stupid
feelings.

128
00:06:10,433 --> 00:06:11,700
[SOBBING]

129
00:06:11,833 --> 00:06:14,000
I'm sorry, Mom.

130
00:06:14,133 --> 00:06:15,567
I'm just scared.

131
00:06:16,367 --> 00:06:19,633
[SOBBING]

132
00:06:19,767 --> 00:06:22,733
[DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING]

133
00:06:22,867 --> 00:06:24,967
I am sorry for yelling at you.

134
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:27,600
But Ashley is our only hope.

135
00:06:29,367 --> 00:06:31,900
And if she can help you,
you will live.

136
00:06:32,733 --> 00:06:36,033
And in some way...

137
00:06:37,167 --> 00:06:42,100
she will be able to repay
the sins of her mother.

138
00:06:42,267 --> 00:06:50,533
[MUSIC CONTINUES...]

139
00:06:50,667 --> 00:06:52,333
Enough, I am sorry! Okay?

140
00:06:52,467 --> 00:06:56,700
- [SOBBING]
- You understand me, right?

141
00:06:56,833 --> 00:07:00,967
- I'm sorry
- [SOBBING]

142
00:07:01,100 --> 00:07:03,033
That's okay.

143
00:07:05,233 --> 00:07:07,767
Dad, I really want to get
tested.

144
00:07:07,900 --> 00:07:09,033
Please.

145
00:07:09,167 --> 00:07:13,167
My child, did you not see what
happened earlier?

146
00:07:15,067 --> 00:07:17,067
You heard my reasons why I do
not what you to get tested.

147
00:07:18,467 --> 00:07:22,000
Ash, our situation
is already complicated.

148
00:07:22,133 --> 00:07:24,033
Let us not make it worse.

149
00:07:25,367 --> 00:07:27,500
But it is just a test.

150
00:07:27,633 --> 00:07:30,433
We will know if we match or not.

151
00:07:30,567 --> 00:07:32,300
There is no operation yet.

152
00:07:32,433 --> 00:07:34,333
No, no, no,
that is not just a simple test.

153
00:07:35,033 --> 00:07:36,700
They will take your blood.

154
00:07:36,833 --> 00:07:38,933
Now, if it matches,

155
00:07:39,067 --> 00:07:40,867
they will interfere
with your body.

156
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:43,167
There will be extraction.

157
00:07:43,300 --> 00:07:44,867
They will insert things

158
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:47,333
and take things
inside your body.

159
00:07:47,500 --> 00:07:50,600
Dad, I am not scared.

160
00:07:50,733 --> 00:07:52,000
I am.

161
00:07:52,133 --> 00:07:53,867
I am the one who is scared,
my child.

162
00:07:55,367 --> 00:07:58,067
Even if they say it is safe,

163
00:07:58,200 --> 00:07:59,400
it is not guaranteed.

164
00:07:59,533 --> 00:08:01,400
And I cannot control that.

165
00:08:01,533 --> 00:08:03,733
And I would not
forgive myself...

166
00:08:05,033 --> 00:08:07,100
if complications happen.

167
00:08:08,033 --> 00:08:10,267
If I were the one
in the hospital bed

168
00:08:11,567 --> 00:08:15,400
and only Jasmine could save me,

169
00:08:15,533 --> 00:08:17,467
would you not beg?

170
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:19,500
Would you not do everything?

171
00:08:19,633 --> 00:08:21,333
I just do not want
someone to die

172
00:08:21,500 --> 00:08:24,067
just because someone
is afraid to try, Dad.

173
00:08:25,900 --> 00:08:27,033
Especially Jasmine,

174
00:08:27,167 --> 00:08:30,033
the one I want to help heal.

175
00:08:30,167 --> 00:08:31,233
[SIGHS]

176
00:08:31,367 --> 00:08:32,800
My child, I did not raise you

177
00:08:32,933 --> 00:08:35,600
to be the savior of other
people's problems.

178
00:08:35,733 --> 00:08:37,400
You are still so young.

179
00:08:39,533 --> 00:08:41,367
And Jasmine is also so young

180
00:08:41,500 --> 00:08:43,733
to be denied a chance
to recover.

181
00:08:43,867 --> 00:08:46,067
I also did not raise you
to turn away

182
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:48,300
when you can help.

183
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,467
But as your parent,

184
00:08:51,700 --> 00:08:55,767
I will not let you enter
a situation that could harm you.

185
00:08:55,933 --> 00:08:56,900
I am sorry, Ash.

186
00:08:57,033 --> 00:08:59,267
If this is not the answer you
wanted to hear.

187
00:08:59,400 --> 00:09:04,233
[DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING]

188
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:08,600
I already begged.

189
00:09:08,733 --> 00:09:11,567
But Edward and Thea
still did not agree.

190
00:09:12,500 --> 00:09:15,233
So, I already talked to Dad.

191
00:09:15,367 --> 00:09:17,767
That was the only thing
you had to do,

192
00:09:17,900 --> 00:09:20,500
and you still could not do it
on your own?

193
00:09:20,633 --> 00:09:22,300
I am doing what I can.

194
00:09:23,933 --> 00:09:26,200
Are you really doing enough?

195
00:09:26,333 --> 00:09:29,367
You hid the truth
for sixteen years.

196
00:09:29,533 --> 00:09:31,400
Now that you have a chance
to make up for it,

197
00:09:31,533 --> 00:09:32,833
you still cannot do anything.

198
00:09:32,967 --> 00:09:34,900
It is not that easy.

199
00:09:35,033 --> 00:09:36,267
They have legal rights.

200
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:40,067
[MACHINE BEEPING]

201
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:42,367
- Jasmine! Jasmine!
- Jasmine?

202
00:09:42,500 --> 00:09:44,067
Jasmine, my child! My child!

203
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,533
- Doctor!
- Call a doctor!

204
00:09:45,667 --> 00:09:47,600
- Doctor!
- My child!

205
00:09:47,733 --> 00:09:49,100
My child, please!

206
00:09:49,233 --> 00:09:50,700
Breathe! My child!

207
00:09:50,833 --> 00:09:53,300
Jasmine! Jasmine!

208
00:09:53,433 --> 00:09:56,333
[MACHINE BEEPING]

209
00:09:56,467 --> 00:09:57,867
Ah, Mrs. Torrecampo.

210
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:59,367
Excuse me, please step
outside for now.

211
00:10:00,300 --> 00:10:02,433
- Jasmine!
- Let us step outside for now.

212
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:04,767
Blood pressure crashing.

213
00:10:04,900 --> 00:10:06,500
Possible septic response.

214
00:10:06,633 --> 00:10:07,667
We need to stabilize
immediately.

215
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:09,233
Nurse, prepare norephedrine.

216
00:10:09,367 --> 00:10:10,667
- Yes, Doctor.
- Move.

217
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:16,467
[INTENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

218
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:23,200
[MUSIC CONTINUES...]

219
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:31,333
[MUSIC CONTINUES...]

220
00:10:33,333 --> 00:10:35,667
[MACHINE BEEPING]

221
00:10:35,833 --> 00:10:43,267
[INTENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

222
00:10:45,300 --> 00:10:51,567
[MUSIC CONTINUES...]

223
00:10:52,933 --> 00:10:54,333
Yes, Dad.

224
00:10:55,633 --> 00:10:58,500
Just text me if we are pushing
through tomorrow, okay?

225
00:10:59,400 --> 00:11:00,900
Okay.

226
00:11:01,033 --> 00:11:02,833
I am heading home anyway.

227
00:11:04,100 --> 00:11:05,400
All right.

228
00:11:05,533 --> 00:11:06,800
Bye.

229
00:11:16,967 --> 00:11:18,767
Hey, Ash.

230
00:11:18,900 --> 00:11:20,600
Called it.

231
00:11:20,733 --> 00:11:23,667
Favorite drink, favorite corner.

232
00:11:23,800 --> 00:11:26,233
This is what you told me
about before.

233
00:11:26,367 --> 00:11:28,400
When you want to disappear
from the world.

234
00:11:33,367 --> 00:11:35,967
So you knew I wanted
to disappear.

235
00:11:36,100 --> 00:11:37,400
Then why are you here?

236
00:11:38,900 --> 00:11:40,900
You know why I have been
avoiding you, right?

237
00:11:41,867 --> 00:11:43,567
To stop this.

238
00:11:43,700 --> 00:11:45,167
To stop whatever this is.

239
00:11:45,300 --> 00:11:46,967
This?

240
00:11:47,100 --> 00:11:48,433
My worrying about you?

241
00:11:48,567 --> 00:11:50,200
Checking if you are okay?

242
00:11:50,333 --> 00:11:51,967
Or 'yung fact na I like you?

243
00:11:52,100 --> 00:11:54,767
Xander, can you just please
stop it?

244
00:11:54,900 --> 00:11:56,067
Stop it!

245
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:58,067
Stop saying what I'm feeling?

246
00:11:58,200 --> 00:12:00,800
That I know you feel too?

247
00:12:00,933 --> 00:12:02,700
If you would just let me prove

248
00:12:02,833 --> 00:12:04,433
that I am worthy
of being liked by you.

249
00:12:07,300 --> 00:12:08,400
[CLEARS THROAT]

250
00:12:10,467 --> 00:12:13,333
You know, having a boyfriend
is not on my mind.

251
00:12:13,467 --> 00:12:15,833
Okay? None.

252
00:12:17,300 --> 00:12:19,433
You know what I want right now?

253
00:12:19,567 --> 00:12:21,800
I just want Jasmine to survive.

254
00:12:21,933 --> 00:12:23,233
That is the only thing that
matters to me right now,

255
00:12:23,367 --> 00:12:24,500
Xander, okay?

256
00:12:24,633 --> 00:12:25,800
I know.

257
00:12:25,933 --> 00:12:27,833
I want her to be okay too.

258
00:12:27,967 --> 00:12:30,133
She's my friend too, Ash.

259
00:12:30,267 --> 00:12:32,300
I am not here to add stress.

260
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:37,000
I just want to be here to help.

261
00:12:37,133 --> 00:12:38,233
To be with you.

262
00:12:39,700 --> 00:12:40,700
Okay.

263
00:12:40,833 --> 00:12:42,433
Even just as a friend for now.

264
00:12:44,567 --> 00:12:46,633
You do not have to wait.

265
00:12:46,767 --> 00:12:48,567
I know.

266
00:12:48,733 --> 00:12:50,600
But I'm not asking for anything.

267
00:12:50,733 --> 00:12:52,900
But please do not push me away.

268
00:12:54,433 --> 00:12:55,433
Okay.

269
00:12:55,567 --> 00:12:57,267
If being friends is all you can
handle right now,

270
00:12:57,400 --> 00:12:59,500
I'm willing to wait for you.

271
00:12:59,633 --> 00:13:00,900
You'll see.

272
00:13:04,967 --> 00:13:08,267
- [KNOCKING]
- Just a moment, coming!

273
00:13:09,533 --> 00:13:10,600
Oh, Ma'am Thea.

274
00:13:10,733 --> 00:13:12,700
- Where is Daddy Greg?
- You are not allowed here.

275
00:13:12,833 --> 00:13:14,033
I need to talk to him.

276
00:13:14,167 --> 00:13:15,333
[CLAMORING]

277
00:13:15,467 --> 00:13:17,200
- You are not allowed, Ma'am.
- Che, Weng!

278
00:13:17,333 --> 00:13:19,233
- Sir.
- Leave us.

279
00:13:19,367 --> 00:13:23,300
[INTENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

280
00:13:23,467 --> 00:13:25,267
What the hell do you want?

281
00:13:25,400 --> 00:13:26,867
I just came from the office

282
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:30,100
and I was surprised to see
all my things already boxed.

283
00:13:30,233 --> 00:13:31,567
What was that? Just like that?

284
00:13:31,700 --> 00:13:33,700
Not even a meeting with HR?

285
00:13:33,833 --> 00:13:35,767
You already kicked us out
in this house.

286
00:13:35,900 --> 00:13:38,067
and now you are firing me too.

287
00:13:38,200 --> 00:13:39,933
You no longer deserve
to be an employee

288
00:13:40,067 --> 00:13:41,367
of Torrecampo Realty.

289
00:13:41,500 --> 00:13:43,067
On what grounds?

290
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:46,467
I did nothing illegal.

291
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:48,700
Trust is currency in business.

292
00:13:48,833 --> 00:13:51,500
And right now,
I no longer trust you.

293
00:13:52,033 --> 00:13:53,733
So, what is this? Personal?

294
00:13:53,867 --> 00:13:56,167
Everything is personal
in business!

295
00:13:56,333 --> 00:13:58,767
So how will I provide
for Ashley now?

296
00:13:58,900 --> 00:14:00,400
She is still your grandchild.

297
00:14:02,067 --> 00:14:05,300
If you want to secure
your child's future...

298
00:14:07,167 --> 00:14:08,900
there is one thing you can do.

299
00:14:10,833 --> 00:14:12,600
Agree to have Ashley tested.

300
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:15,233
[HUFFS]

301
00:14:15,367 --> 00:14:16,700
Of course!

302
00:14:16,833 --> 00:14:19,200
Your favorite child
tattled to you.

303
00:14:19,667 --> 00:14:22,433
I thought he was not the loser
between him and Edward.

304
00:14:23,300 --> 00:14:24,400
What is this?

305
00:14:24,533 --> 00:14:26,667
Having his father fix his mess

306
00:14:26,800 --> 00:14:29,567
while he does not care
about his other child?

307
00:14:29,733 --> 00:14:31,567
It's just a test.

308
00:14:31,700 --> 00:14:33,600
If they do not match,
life goes on.

309
00:14:33,733 --> 00:14:37,500
But if they match,
she will donate to Jasmine.

310
00:14:37,633 --> 00:14:41,200
You are using my child
as payment for my sins?

311
00:14:41,333 --> 00:14:43,533
I am not using my grandchild.

312
00:14:43,667 --> 00:14:46,933
That is her role now
as part of the family.

313
00:14:48,367 --> 00:14:50,367
Just like you, Thea.

314
00:14:50,500 --> 00:14:53,400
If you still want to be part
of the Torrecampo family.

315
00:14:53,533 --> 00:14:55,033
So, everything
is conditional now?

316
00:14:55,167 --> 00:14:57,100
If I do not agree,
I have no job,

317
00:14:57,233 --> 00:14:58,700
I have no support,
that is it?

318
00:14:58,833 --> 00:15:00,267
I'm not a charity.

319
00:15:01,133 --> 00:15:02,567
I run an empire.

320
00:15:02,733 --> 00:15:06,167
And an empire
does not carry liabilities.

321
00:15:06,300 --> 00:15:07,767
So if you want anything left
of you, Thea

322
00:15:07,900 --> 00:15:11,400
and your child,
agree to have Ashley tested.

323
00:15:13,900 --> 00:15:17,667
[INTENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

324
00:15:17,800 --> 00:15:21,900
Everything will be easy
if you just comply.

325
00:15:22,033 --> 00:15:29,033
[MUSIC CONTINUES...]

326
00:15:31,033 --> 00:15:33,000
Mr. and Mrs. Torrecampo,

327
00:15:33,133 --> 00:15:35,100
we were able to avoid
septic shock.

328
00:15:35,267 --> 00:15:38,133
But her immune system
is extremely weak.

329
00:15:38,267 --> 00:15:41,200
The window is closing,
and if you know

330
00:15:41,333 --> 00:15:45,033
any potential donors,
we really need to move soon.

331
00:15:45,167 --> 00:15:46,533
I will leave you for now.

332
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:49,533
Did you hear that?

333
00:15:49,667 --> 00:15:52,067
We are running out of time,
do something!

334
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:53,367
Marj, I am doing everything
I can...

335
00:15:53,500 --> 00:15:56,600
If you need to plead with
Ashley, then plead.

336
00:15:56,733 --> 00:15:58,900
We need parental consent.

337
00:15:59,633 --> 00:16:01,300
Where is what your father
promised, huh?

338
00:16:01,433 --> 00:16:03,400
You rarely do the right thing,

339
00:16:03,533 --> 00:16:04,500
and still nothing.

340
00:16:05,967 --> 00:16:08,800
Marj, we are all doing
the best we can.

341
00:16:08,967 --> 00:16:10,300
Well, it is not enough!

342
00:16:11,033 --> 00:16:13,333
If you need to plead
with Thea, do it!

343
00:16:13,467 --> 00:16:14,867
Even if she is your mistress,

344
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:17,700
even if she is the reason
our family fell apart,

345
00:16:17,833 --> 00:16:20,000
I no longer care
about your relationship!

346
00:16:20,133 --> 00:16:23,000
I no longer care
what else gets thrown in my face

347
00:16:23,133 --> 00:16:25,633
because I want my child to live!

348
00:16:25,767 --> 00:16:28,100
I can live
with you deceiving me

349
00:16:28,233 --> 00:16:29,500
rather than lose my child.

350
00:16:29,633 --> 00:16:31,633
Do you understand that?

351
00:16:31,767 --> 00:16:34,367
I do not want to lose Jasmine.

352
00:16:34,500 --> 00:16:37,567
[BACKGROUND CHATTER]

353
00:16:37,700 --> 00:16:40,033
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

354
00:16:40,167 --> 00:16:42,533
[SOBBING]

355
00:16:43,900 --> 00:16:47,933
[DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING]

356
00:16:48,067 --> 00:16:50,633
[BACKGROUND CHATTER]

357
00:16:52,533 --> 00:17:02,500
[MUSIC CONTINUES...]

358
00:17:07,200 --> 00:17:10,033
<i>If you want to secure
your child's future,</i>

359
00:17:10,167 --> 00:17:11,433
<i> agree to have Ashley tested.</i>

360
00:17:11,567 --> 00:17:14,200
<i>Everything will be easy
if you just comply.</i>

361
00:17:14,333 --> 00:17:16,400
<i>I will not let you
enter a situation</i>

362
00:17:16,567 --> 00:17:17,833
<i> that could harm you.</i>

363
00:17:17,967 --> 00:17:20,367
<i>I am sorry, Ash, if this is not
the answer you wanted to hear.</i>

364
00:17:20,900 --> 00:17:22,533
<i> I really want to get tested.</i>

365
00:17:22,900 --> 00:17:23,867
<i> Please.</i>

366
00:17:24,233 --> 00:17:34,167
[DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING]

367
00:17:37,367 --> 00:17:39,100
- [SOBS]
- Mom?

368
00:17:40,233 --> 00:17:41,633
Are you crying?

369
00:17:43,133 --> 00:17:44,867
What's wrong this time?

370
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:46,033
Nothing, my child.

371
00:17:47,133 --> 00:17:48,133
Nothing.

372
00:17:51,167 --> 00:17:53,167
Do you think it is right to...

373
00:17:54,133 --> 00:17:55,100
To what, Mom?

374
00:17:56,700 --> 00:18:00,633
Do you really want
to help Jasmine?

375
00:18:02,700 --> 00:18:03,767
Yes.

376
00:18:04,800 --> 00:18:10,067
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

377
00:18:12,500 --> 00:18:13,800
Paolo, have you contacted him
again?

378
00:18:14,900 --> 00:18:17,167
I told you, what your father did
was not right.

379
00:18:18,433 --> 00:18:20,500
I have not spoken to him again
because...

380
00:18:21,400 --> 00:18:23,133
You do not need to talk anymore.

381
00:18:24,700 --> 00:18:25,833
Consent form.

382
00:18:28,867 --> 00:18:34,867
[INTENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

383
00:18:35,967 --> 00:18:38,067
I am agreeing
to have Ashley tested.

384
00:18:41,633 --> 00:18:42,533
Ashley.

385
00:18:42,667 --> 00:18:43,967
Do not thank me yet.

386
00:18:45,067 --> 00:18:46,167
This is just a test.

387
00:18:47,400 --> 00:18:49,033
And Edward does not know
about this.

388
00:18:49,167 --> 00:18:55,667
[INTENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

389
00:18:55,833 --> 00:18:56,567
And I just want
to make this clear.

390
00:18:57,900 --> 00:18:59,767
If Ashley turns out
to be a match,

391
00:18:59,900 --> 00:19:03,867
that does not mean
she will automatically donate.

392
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:05,467
It will still be
Ashley's decision.

393
00:19:07,200 --> 00:19:09,467
And if she says no,

394
00:19:09,600 --> 00:19:12,233
this discussion ends here.

395
00:19:12,367 --> 00:19:14,100
I will not allow my child
to be pressured.

396
00:19:14,700 --> 00:19:16,367
No matter who it is for.

397
00:19:18,433 --> 00:19:26,067
[INTENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

398
00:19:31,300 --> 00:19:33,633
This is just a simple blood
draw, Ashley.

399
00:19:34,767 --> 00:19:37,067
Just a small prick.

400
00:19:37,200 --> 00:19:38,900
- Okay?
- Okay.

401
00:19:42,567 --> 00:19:43,567
[SIGHS]

402
00:19:47,133 --> 00:19:48,167
Are you ready?

403
00:19:48,300 --> 00:19:49,733
Take a deep breath.

404
00:19:57,067 --> 00:19:58,233
I am ready.

405
00:19:58,367 --> 00:20:07,200
[INTENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

406
00:20:07,367 --> 00:20:17,333
[MUSIC CONTINUES...]

407
00:20:23,700 --> 00:20:30,100
[DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING]

408
00:20:32,433 --> 00:20:33,433
Thank you.

409
00:20:33,567 --> 00:20:34,567
Thank you.

410
00:20:34,700 --> 00:20:43,367
[MUSIC CONTINUES...]

411
00:20:47,167 --> 00:20:48,600
Thank you, Ashley.

412
00:20:50,633 --> 00:20:52,600
It is just a test.

413
00:20:52,733 --> 00:20:54,333
Even so, it is still not easy.

414
00:20:55,533 --> 00:20:57,767
Especially after everything
that happened.

415
00:21:01,567 --> 00:21:03,867
I am not doing this for you.

416
00:21:07,733 --> 00:21:09,267
This is for Jas.

417
00:21:11,467 --> 00:21:13,400
Even before I found out

418
00:21:13,533 --> 00:21:14,933
that we are siblings.

419
00:21:17,467 --> 00:21:19,533
I really love Jas.

420
00:21:22,267 --> 00:21:24,500
I see her as more than a cousin.

421
00:21:26,767 --> 00:21:28,767
Actually, we are not okay
right now.

422
00:21:30,967 --> 00:21:32,800
But even if we have issues...

423
00:21:35,367 --> 00:21:37,267
I cannot abandon her.

424
00:21:40,467 --> 00:21:42,433
You know, you are lucky
to have Edward.

425
00:21:44,333 --> 00:21:45,433
He raised you well.

426
00:21:47,467 --> 00:21:49,233
Whatever I lacked
as a father to you,

427
00:21:49,367 --> 00:21:52,867
he made up for it.

428
00:21:55,567 --> 00:21:58,700
I cannot compare

429
00:21:58,833 --> 00:22:03,300
to the kind of father
he was to you.

430
00:22:03,433 --> 00:22:12,167
[DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING]

431
00:22:19,600 --> 00:22:23,933
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

432
00:22:24,067 --> 00:22:27,400
Wasn't your plan with Ashley
supposed to be tonight?

433
00:22:28,667 --> 00:22:30,367
I arrived earlier than expected.

434
00:22:30,500 --> 00:22:32,400
Where did you come from?

435
00:22:32,533 --> 00:22:35,433
Ah, we just went out to eat.

436
00:22:36,833 --> 00:22:38,900
Can I not have time to bond
with my child?

437
00:22:41,667 --> 00:22:42,567
I thought...

438
00:22:42,700 --> 00:22:43,667
What did you think?

439
00:22:44,833 --> 00:22:46,000
Nothing.

440
00:22:48,400 --> 00:22:50,833
Next time, please let me know
so I do not worry.

441
00:22:52,467 --> 00:22:53,367
So, Ashley,

442
00:22:53,500 --> 00:22:55,000
do you want to leave now?

443
00:22:56,000 --> 00:22:58,267
Ashley will freshen up first,

444
00:22:58,400 --> 00:22:59,833
then meet you in the lobby.

445
00:23:01,700 --> 00:23:02,933
Okay.

446
00:23:03,067 --> 00:23:08,167
[MUSIC CONTINUES...]

447
00:23:08,300 --> 00:23:09,567
[SIGHS]

448
00:23:10,267 --> 00:23:11,300
Mom.

449
00:23:11,667 --> 00:23:14,033
Are we not going to tell Papa
about this?

450
00:23:15,033 --> 00:23:16,767
My child, do not.

451
00:23:17,300 --> 00:23:19,967
We are not even sure yet
if you are really a match.

452
00:23:20,700 --> 00:23:21,967
But Papa...

453
00:23:22,133 --> 00:23:23,767
My child, please.

454
00:23:23,900 --> 00:23:26,433
If you truly want to help
Jasmine,

455
00:23:26,567 --> 00:23:28,067
stand by that.

456
00:23:29,000 --> 00:23:30,267
But there is a condition.

457
00:23:31,333 --> 00:23:33,300
You cannot tell your father.

458
00:23:33,433 --> 00:23:35,800
He will surely get angry
if you disobey him.

459
00:23:39,533 --> 00:23:43,200
What matters is that you already
got tested.

460
00:23:44,167 --> 00:23:45,467
I just hope you do not match

461
00:23:45,600 --> 00:23:47,833
so our part is over.

462
00:23:49,267 --> 00:23:51,533
Our part?

463
00:23:51,667 --> 00:23:53,800
And should I not match?

464
00:23:55,200 --> 00:23:57,900
We did this to support
Jasmine, right?

465
00:24:00,467 --> 00:24:01,533
Yes.

466
00:24:02,067 --> 00:24:03,667
It is enough that you helped.

467
00:24:06,300 --> 00:24:07,867
Go on now, follow your father.

468
00:24:08,000 --> 00:24:17,833
[INTENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

469
00:24:17,967 --> 00:24:22,867
[MUSIC CONTINUES...]

470
00:24:24,867 --> 00:24:27,800
[MACHINE BEEPING]

471
00:24:29,100 --> 00:24:30,267
[SMOOCHES]

472
00:24:30,400 --> 00:24:31,867
Marj.

473
00:24:34,567 --> 00:24:35,967
What? Is there a result already?

474
00:24:36,100 --> 00:24:37,533
What did the doctor say?

475
00:24:37,667 --> 00:24:39,000
We have a donor.

476
00:24:39,133 --> 00:24:42,567
[INTENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

477
00:24:42,700 --> 00:24:44,100
Ashley matched with her?

478
00:24:44,233 --> 00:24:49,667
[MUSIC CONTINUES...]

479
00:24:53,967 --> 00:24:55,900
Are they still pressuring you
about the test?

480
00:24:56,033 --> 00:24:59,633
Maybe you are still giving them
hope and accommodating them?

481
00:24:59,767 --> 00:25:02,167
Can you endure Jasmine's
condition getting worse?

482
00:25:02,333 --> 00:25:03,567
If Ashley were the one
who was sick,

483
00:25:03,700 --> 00:25:06,067
I feel Paolo would not
hesitate...

484
00:25:06,200 --> 00:25:08,333
- [THUMPS]
- Thea, one mistake

485
00:25:08,467 --> 00:25:10,933
in the operating room
we and our child will carry

486
00:25:11,067 --> 00:25:12,033
that for life.

487
00:25:12,167 --> 00:25:13,533
Do you want Ashley to be harmed?

488
00:25:13,667 --> 00:25:15,100
Are you avoiding us?

489
00:25:15,233 --> 00:25:16,100
Marj, I'm sorry.

490
00:25:16,233 --> 00:25:17,733
We are not agreeing to the test.

491
00:25:17,867 --> 00:25:20,600
Edward, they already got tested.

492
00:25:20,733 --> 00:25:21,733
What?

493
00:25:24,167 --> 00:25:25,500
You got tested behind my back?

494
00:25:25,633 --> 00:25:27,367
So we are just going
to let Jas be?

495
00:25:27,500 --> 00:25:28,667
You're just gonna let her die?

496
00:25:28,800 --> 00:25:30,267
If it were not because of you,

497
00:25:30,400 --> 00:25:32,033
everything would not have
fallen apart.

498
00:25:32,167 --> 00:25:34,100
The cheating, everything,

499
00:25:34,233 --> 00:25:36,267
even what happened to Uncle
Jobert.

500
00:25:36,433 --> 00:25:38,200
- [SLAPS]
- Enough!

501
00:25:38,333 --> 00:25:39,667
Thea!

502
00:25:39,800 --> 00:25:42,167
Honestly, Ashley,
your mother makes decisions

503
00:25:42,300 --> 00:25:43,433
when she's cornered.

504
00:25:43,567 --> 00:25:45,900
When something needs to be
protected,

505
00:25:46,033 --> 00:25:47,633
when something needs to be
hidden,

506
00:25:47,767 --> 00:25:51,033
people only change their minds
when they are forced to face

507
00:25:51,167 --> 00:25:52,400
what they are avoiding.

508
00:25:52,533 --> 00:25:55,433
What if there is really
something they need to face?

509
00:25:55,567 --> 00:25:57,367
I can no longer stay silent.

510
00:25:57,500 --> 00:25:59,500
If I need to tell the truth

511
00:25:59,633 --> 00:26:03,333
to save Jasmine,
I will do it.

512
00:26:03,467 --> 00:26:06,933
[INTENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

513
00:26:07,067 --> 00:26:08,133
You don't get it.

514
00:26:08,300 --> 00:26:09,333
This is karma.

515
00:26:09,467 --> 00:26:11,633
Your karma is that your child
might die

516
00:26:11,767 --> 00:26:12,867
because you are greedy,

517
00:26:13,000 --> 00:26:14,900
deceitful, and arrogant.

518
00:26:15,033 --> 00:26:15,900
[THUDS]

519
00:26:16,033 --> 00:26:17,000
Once this is fixed,

520
00:26:17,133 --> 00:26:18,733
we can finally leave this mess.

521
00:26:18,867 --> 00:26:20,500
They will not easily
take you from me.

522
00:26:20,633 --> 00:26:23,033
I am scared, Mom.

523
00:26:23,167 --> 00:26:24,300
[SQUEALS]

524
00:26:25,133 --> 00:26:27,267
[LOUD CRASH]
